EN: I am learning to play the piano.

ZH: 钢琴是我最喜欢的乐器之一。
EN: The piano is one of my favorite instruments.

ZH: 他每天都练习弹钢琴。
EN: He practices playing the piano every day.

ZH: 她的钢琴演奏技巧非常优秀。
EN: Her piano playing skills are excellent.

ZH: 我在音乐学校学习弹钢琴。
EN: I study piano at music school.

ZH: 这个音乐厅有一架优美的黑色钢琴。
EN: The concert hall has a beautiful black piano.

ZH: 我梦想着有一天能够弹奏一曲著名的钢琴曲。
EN: I dream of being able to play a famous piano piece one day.

ZH: 她在音乐比赛中表演了一首自己弹奏的钢琴曲。
EN: She performed a piano piece that she played herself at the music competition.

ZH: 这架钢琴的音质非常清脆动人。
EN: The sound quality of this piano is very crisp and moving.

ZH: 他在音乐学院学习钢琴演奏。
EN: He is studying piano performance at the music academy.

ZH: 钢琴的琴键需要经常保养。
EN: The piano keys need regular maintenance.

ZH: 这座城市有一家著名的钢琴厂。
EN: This city has a famous piano factory.

ZH: 我们家客厅里摆放着一架钢琴。
EN: There is a piano in our living room.

ZH: 这首歌的伴奏是由钢琴演奏的。
EN: The accompaniment of this song is played on the piano.

ZH: 钢琴音乐能让人心情放松。
EN: Piano music can relax your mood.

ZH: 喜欢弹钢琴是我的兴趣之一。
EN: Playing the piano is one of my hobbies.

ZH: 我用钢琴谱来练习新的音乐。
EN: I use piano sheet music to practice new songs.

ZH: 钢琴的琴弦需要经常调整。
EN: The strings of the piano need to be adjusted regularly.

ZH: 她堂兄在音乐学校主修钢琴演奏。
EN: Her cousin majors in piano performance at music school.

ZH: 他在家里继承了一架古老的钢琴。
EN: He inherited an old piano at home.
